    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/da4434e1f318199a8e7928462518de73.avif?t=1771717820\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Dare to Enter</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shed Skin, Bleed Ink </strong>is a visually striking, boundary-breaking, experimental game where you explore—or confine—your identity by carving sigils into your flesh under the guidance of the Overseer. Your ultimate goal: to reincarnate as the Prophet in perfect alignment with the Observatory's sacred vision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But to escape this cycle, you may need to look beyond the stars and deep into the files of this ritual...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/4665ecd5b8f59afaa568701fd57b2030.avif?t=1771717820\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Key Features</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >=<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/1caae92644be5bb0c189e2cd24efc979.poster.avif?t=1771717820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/1caae92644be5bb0c189e2cd24efc979.webm?t=1771717820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/1caae92644be5bb0c189e2cd24efc979.mp4?t=1771717820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Find Sigils in a Fragmented Reality</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter a surreal realm transcending space and time, where broken realities collide. Each sigil you find is a piece of the sacred puzzle. Now, every decision you make will shape the reincarnation. Analyze and choose carefully—each sigil carries weight in the rebirth of the Prophet.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Inscribe Sigils on Your Flesh</strong> <br><strong></strong><br><br>To forge the connection with the Prophet, you’ll inscribe sigils onto your <strong><i>physical skin</i></strong>, bridging the gap between the digital and the physical world.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/7fb1beefc6ec5a036300659031e95f12.avif?t=1771717820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras_big/7fb1beefc6ec5a036300659031e95f12.avif?t=1771717820 width=800 height=224 /></span><strong>Experience a Visually Striking Digital Ritual</strong> <br><strong></strong><br><br>Immerse yourself in a visually intense, 3D experimental world with sequences designed to provoke thought and challenge perception. (Warning: Some scenes may cause heavy eye strain.)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290150/extras/7ab2953488bff52df1a8f8cefbcf8067.avif?t=1771717820\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Developers</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In creating the game for Peter Brinson's Intermediate course at USC, the developers aimed to make something weird and unique. They invite you to this boundary-pushing experience to explore identity in a new way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
